<h2 id="section-top">General Surgery</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1155">Salford Royal NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent7b39dc55a57647febe3257f6b227a81b">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="theatre lights" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=10151"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>We are committed to providing the highest possible quality of patient care and services.  We believe that each individual is unique, having his or her own physical, psychological, cultural and social needs.   </p>
<p>We believe in patient centred care approach that is designed to maximize the quality of life.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel name-thingsshouldknowmodule">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Things you should know</h3>
<p>We aim for a standard of excellence in the care of our patients and believe that each individual patient should be given the opportunity to receive health education and support in order to maintain a good quality of life within their community.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
